          <li>2011 Roberts, S. <a href="http://media.sethroberts.net/articles/2011 The reception of my self-experimentation.pdf">The reception of my self-experimentation.</a> <em>Journal of Business Research</em>, in press.</li>
          <li>2010 Roberts, S. <a href="http://www.fourhourworkweek.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/Alternative-to-Dieting.pdf"> An alternative to dieting: The body-fat set point and Shangri-La.</a> On the website for Tim Ferriss, <em>The Four-Hour Body</em>.</li>
          <li>2010 Roberts, S. <a href="http://www.fourhourworkweek.com/blog/2010/12/18/the-value-of-self-experimentation-plus-extreme-videos-do-not-try-this-at-home/"> The value of self-experimentation</a>. In Tim Ferriss, <em>The Four-Hour Body</em>. New York: Crown Archtype.</li>
